  "prompt": "Does blind person from birth dream?",
  "response": "Yes, blind people from birth do dream. However, the nature of their dreams can be different from those of sighted individuals. Since they have no visual experiences, their dreams are often composed of other sensory experiences, such as sounds, touch, smell, and emotional sensations. Dreams for those blind from birth are rich in these non-visual sensory details, and they may navigate their dream world using these senses just as they do in waking life.",
